## Patterns & Templates

### Pattern 1: Glassmorphism Card

**When to use:** Modern, premium aesthetic (works well with colorful backgrounds)

```tsx
function GlassCard({ children, className = '' }: GlassCardProps) {
  return (
    <div className={`
      relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
